386
00:22:47,115 --> 00:22:50,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya benar. Kau sepertinya pernah menangis berkali-kali.</font>

387
00:22:51,180 --> 00:22:54,669
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu kau menjadi seperti Lee Shi Kyung.</font>

388
00:22:54,669 --> 00:22:56,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku, ya.</font>

389
00:22:56,470 --> 00:23:00,290
