390
00:23:00,290 --> 00:23:01,791
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu hal yang baik.</font>

391
00:23:01,791 --> 00:23:03,323
<font color=#FFFF00>Lihat itu. Lihat itu.</font>

392
00:23:04,071 --> 00:23:06,021
<font color=#FFFF00>Kim Bom, tunggu!</font>

393
00:23:06,021 --> 00:23:07,044
<font color=#FFFF00>Kim Bom.</font>

394
00:23:07,044 --> 00:23:09,192
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu.</font>

395
00:23:10,554 --> 00:23:13,055
<font color=#FFFF00>Bicara padaku. Berbicaralah denganku.</font>

396
00:23:13,055 --> 00:23:14,815
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak ingin berbicara denganmu.</font>

397
00:23:14,815 --> 00:23:16,144
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kamu seperti ini?</font>

398
00:23:16,144 --> 00:23:19,653
