409
00:23:46,065 --> 00:23:47,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Cemburu apanya?</font>

410
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:48,752
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak punya siapapun.</font>

411
00:23:48,752 --> 00:23:52,576
