430
00:25:32,134 --> 00:25:33,439
<font color=#FFFF00>Misi ini adalah...</font>

431
00:25:33,439 --> 00:25:35,476
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku tidak penasaran.</i></font>

432
00:25:35,476 --> 00:25:37,047
<font color=#FFFF00>Dengarkanlah bahkan jika kau tidak penasaran.</font>

433
00:25:37,047 --> 00:25:38,980
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Hah? Dia bisa membaca pikiranku.</i></font>

434
00:25:40,786 --> 00:25:42,865
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau kenal pasien Kim Jae Woong di rumah sakit?</font>

435
00:25:42,865 --> 00:25:45,695
